1. Web container is a java based web application which provides runtime support required for web applications
which are installed in a server application.

2.Diff bw web server and application server
A web server provides a web container which provides services of a web server
to web applocation.
An appplication server provides services to both web and ejb components.
This provide suppotto both web application and enterprise application.

3. Stateless means it doesnot allow ordoes not store a client information at server side.


